                "name": "David M. Prus",
                "href": "/profile/David-M-Prus"
            },
            "answer_text": "To a point. Our history is a bloody one, where racism, oppression, and violence have marred our progress. Our nation was founded on conquest. However, no one should be punished for the actions of their ancestors, and we\u2019re not alone in having a shameful past. Most countries have legacies of violence and hate. We are a great nation because it WAS the past, and not the present. No more countries being burned and conquered, no more people being enslaved, no more wars of genocide. Our history is our past, but our past does not define our future. We must recognize our sins, but know how to do good and avoid it. Like the Germans, we must always remember our crimes and do our best to be better than we were, and there\u2019s nothing stopping us. ",
